# Loader

Loading indicators communicate to the user that a time-consuming operation, roughly one second or longer, is taking place.

IDS Loader supports the following States: Progress circle, Progress bar, Activity spinner

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/loader
```

```tsx
import { Loader } from '@ids-ts/loader';
```

## Props

### Activity (Spinner)

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `shape` | `'dots' \| 'bar'` | No | Visual style of the loader. |
| `size` | `'small' \| 'medium' \| 'large'` | No | Size of the loader indicator. |
| `automationId` | `string` | No | Test automation identifier. |

